## Import



An existing resource can be imported using its type token, name, and identifier, e.g.

```sh
$ pulumi import azure-native:datashare:BlobFolderDataSet dataset1 /subscriptions/{subscriptionId}/resourceGroups/{resourceGroupName}/providers/Microsoft.DataShare/accounts/{accountName}/shares/{shareName}/dataSets/{dataSetName} 
```


To learn more about importing existing cloud resources, see [Importing resources](/docs/using-pulumi/adopting-pulumi/import/).
